<li><a href="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=4726633" class="external text" title="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=4726633" rel="nofollow">Folk Legend Pete Seeger Looks Back</a> - <a href="/wiki/National_Public_Radio" title="National Public Radio">National Public Radio</a> interview, July 2, 2005</li>
