<li><a href="http://www.harvardsquarelibrary.org/unitarians/seeger.html" class="external text" title="http://www.harvardsquarelibrary.org/unitarians/seeger.html" rel="nofollow">Pete Seeger, Folk Singer and Song Writer</a> by Thomas Blair. Part of a series of Notable American Unitarians</li>
<li><a href="http://www.downhomeradioshow.com/2007/10/interview-with-pete-seeger-down-home-turns-1/" class="external text" title="http://www.downhomeradioshow.com/2007/10/interview-with-pete-seeger-down-home-turns-1/" rel="nofollow">1-hour Internet radio interview</a>- Seeger discusses the music industry, the world in general, and more (August 2007).</li>
<li><a href="http://worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n50-6375" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n50-6375" rel="nofollow">Works by or about Pete Seeger</a> in libraries (<a href="/wiki/WorldCat" title="WorldCat">WorldCat</a> catalog)</li>
